snippet.title: Bob the Robber 2 Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Levels 1 - 11 walkthrough.

Is the city in danger again? This looks like another job for our hero -- robber Bob! Angry dogs, watchful securities and cameras, laser gratings and ... zombies!!! Help Bob to save the city from Gamp corporation!
